QuestData.Title: Tina's Tasteful Tiara
QuestData.Description: It's a dazzling diamond tiara. Who in the valley would be wealthy enough to own such a piece of jewelry?$B$BWhoever it is, they might be willing to give a nice reward.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Tasteful Tiara to Tina Mudclaw at Haohan's House or Halfhill Market in the Valley of the Four Winds.
